description: Naked Kombat is proud to present the beginning of our 2014 Summer Smackdown Tournament. Starting off the elimination matches we have Dirk "The Claymore" Caber taking on Jessie "Cut-Throat" Colter as they battle balls to the wall for a chance to move one step closer to the gold belt. These two muscled hunks have fought before, with Claymore owning Cut-Throat's ass in the sex round. With the points so close before, what better time for a rematch? Claymore is confident he can beat his opponent just as easy as the last time, and plans on leaving Cut-Throat in the gutter before kicking his ass out of the tournament. Cut-Throat isn't going down without a fight though, he has his eyes fixed on redemption and plans on showing Claymore who the real winner is with a load of cum to his face.
title: FIRST ELIMINATION MATCH OF OUR SUMMER SMACKDOWN TOURNAMENT!!!
